data.description: Welcome Home to Comfort and Convenience! This meticulously maintained 2-story gem nestled in a peaceful cul-de-sac offers the perfect blend of modern comfort and thoughtful design. Augusta Woods offers amenities that include sidewalks, a playground and 2 pools! With 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and 1794 square feet of living space, this home is just the right size. Step inside to discover an inviting open-concept layout, where the spacious living area seamlessly flows into the dining space and kitchen. Perfect for entertaining or relaxing with loved ones, this airy atmosphere is bathed in natural light. Upstairs, a loft area awaits, offering flexibility for your lifestyle needs - whether it's a home office, playroom, or relaxation spot. The master bedroom is a true retreat, with a garden tub/shower combo, convenient walk-in closet, and ample space to unwind after a long day. The laundry is conveniently located upstairs. Plus, every corner of this home reflects the care and attention of its meticulous owner, ensuring a move-in-ready experience like no other. Step outside and enjoy the charm of a covered front porch, perfect for sipping your morning coffee or watching the sunset. With the serenity of your cul-de-sac lot, offering privacy and tranquility, you'll love the sense of community and peace this location provides. Augusta Woods offers amenities that include underground utilities sidewalks, a playground and 2 pools! Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this meticulously maintained oasis your own. Schedule your showing today and experience the comfort and charm of this exceptional home!
